These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Sport      | sailing    | handball  | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, almond-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, pakistani
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the turkish is on the far left##1
3. the turkish is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | lemonade     | almond-milk      |
| Nationality   | turkish | indonesian | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: pear, cauliflower, pumpkin
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | coffee | almond-milk  | mirinda       |
| Food       | pear     | cauliflower | pumpkin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, carrot, lime
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, filmmaking, board-games
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | lime    | carrot     | kiwi |
| Hobby   | board-games | skydiving | filmmaking     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, cat, goat
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, bus
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the goat##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | cat | dog     | goat |
| Transport   | bus        | jet-ski | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, spinach, onion
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bike, scooter
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person eating onion is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | onion | zucchini      | spinach  |
| Transport   | subway       | bike | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, soul
3 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, dog
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of d&b is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | ambient     | d&b    |
| Pet           | pony | dog | mouse |

 #################################

 
