.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, camping, fishing
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, pony
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | fishing | camping | board-games  |
| Pet     | pony     | chinchilla      | hamster |

