.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, family, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | coffee   | juice    | water    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | thriller | spy |

