.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, indie, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, turkish
1. the fan of r&b is the colombian##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the turkish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | blues | r&b   | indie  |
| Nationality   | turkish    | colombian | brazilian |

