.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, peas, eggplant
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, analyst, pilot
1. the analyst is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating eggplant is in the middle##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | potato     | eggplant   | peas     |
| Job    | pilot | analyst | software-developer |

