The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, country, r&b
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | almond-milk | tea  |
| Music-Genre   | country | r&b   | metal |

