.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, orange, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person eating pineapple is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | orange | watermelon   | pineapple        |
| Sport   | cricket    | surfing | biathlon |

