The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, funk, classical
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | reading | puzzles | photography |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | classical     | funk  |

