.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, pomegranate, kale
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | kale | radish       | pomegranate  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | cricket | swimming |

 